### 12. 修改节点基础信息与参数校验
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{managedProjectId}}/nodes/{{nodeId1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "需求分析与确认",
  "description": "更新后的需求分析阶段",
